results.cleanName: Black and White Theme Deck Green Tornado Serperior

extendedData.name: CardText
extendedData.value:
Play the Green Tornado theme deck to blow away the opposition while sheltering your own Pokmon with Serperior's Leaf Storm attack! Then, bring Sawsbuck into the action and overwhelm your opponent's Pokemon with its "the greener, the meaner" Nature Power attack! And if your opponents can weather the storm with tough Pokemon, let them ride it out in peaceful slumbers with Musharna's Hypnotic Ray attack! With the Green Tornado theme deck, will you whirl your way to victory?

Contents:
1 60-card preconstructed deck
Damage counters
1 coin

results.name: Black & White Theme Deck - "Green Tornado" [Serperior]

results.cleanName: Black and White Theme Deck Red Frenzy Emboar

extendedData.name: CardText
extendedData.value:
Unleash a firestorm in the Red Frenzy theme deck with the mighty Mega Fire Pig Pokemon Emboar! Feeling burned out after its tremendous Flare Blitz attack? Well fan the flames with the Energy Retrieval Trainer card and reignite with Emboar's Heat Crash attack! Then add fuel to the fire and insult to injury with Stoutland's Giga Impact attack! Let your opponents feel the heat when you play the Red Frenzy theme deck!

Contents:
1 60-card preconstructed deck
Damage counters
1 coin

results.name: Black & White Theme Deck - "Red Frenzy" [Emboar]

results.cleanName: Black and White Theme Deck Blue Assault Samurott

extendedData.name: CardText
extendedData.value:
Your opponents will soon find themselves in troubled waters with the Blue Assault theme deck, especially when you unleash Galvantula! Its Electroweb attack is sure to leave them in sticky situations, and its Leech Life attack will keep your own Pokmon going strong! Use Basculin's Crunch attack to leave your opponent's Pokmon high and dry while Professor Juniper brings you calm waters. Will you be able to batter the opposition with the Blue Assault theme deck?

Contents:
1 60-card preconstructed deck
Damage counters
1 coin

Plus, you get five booster packs from the Black & White expansion series, and a specially selected foil promo card to add to your collection, giving you even more Pokemon to take with you to your next victory!
